                            <comment id="12711825" author="ryanobjc" created="Thu, 21 May 2009 21:37:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One other thing, if hbase.regionserver.dns.interface isnt set, we should use &apos;hostname&apos; - there are standard Java APIs to determine this.  Look in the hadoop net code.  If dns.nameserver is not set, we should use the system-default as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For people who are satisified with &apos;hostname&apos; as the accurate IP for their host, don&apos;t make them set extra config.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
